      "code_html": "<table class=\"ws-table-all notranslate\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th style=\"width:15%\">Operator</th>\n<th style=\"width:20%\">Name</th>\n<th style=\"width:35%\">Description</th>\n<th style=\"width:20%\">Example</th>\n<th style=\"width:10%\">Try it</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&amp;&amp;\u00a0</td>\n<td>Logical and</td>\n<td>Returns true if both statements are true</td>\n<td>x &lt; 5 &amp;&amp;\u00a0 x &lt; 10</td>\n<td><a class=\"w3-btn btnsmall btnsmall\" href=\"trykotlin.php?filename=demo_oper_logical1\" target=\"_blank\">Try it \u00bb</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>||\u00a0</td>\n<td>Logical or</td>\n<td>Returns true if one of the statements is true</td>\n<td>x &lt; 5 || x &lt; 4</td>\n<td><a class=\"w3-btn btnsmall btnsmall\" href=\"trykotlin.php?filename=demo_oper_logical2\" target=\"_blank\">Try it \u00bb</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>!</td>\n<td>Logical not</td>\n<td>Reverse the result, returns false if the result is true</td>\n<td></td>\n<td><a class=\"w3-btn btnsmall btnsmall\" href=\"trykotlin.php?filename=demo_oper_logical3\" target=\"_blank\">Try it \u00bb</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>",
